Package socialmedia

Class Account

java.lang.Object
socialmedia.Account
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
Direct Known Subclasses:
Post
public class Account extends Object implements Serializable
This class stores information of each Account in the social media platform. Accounts can be created or removed and their description field can be updated. This class is a superclass of Posts and Comments classes.
Author:
Aisha, Saida
